channel.title: Bankruptcy Court Eastern District of Wisconsin - New items on govinfo
channel.description: Provides access to newly published GovInfo content from the Bankruptcy Court Eastern District of Wisconsin . United States Courts Opinions (USCOURTS) collection is a project between the U.S. Government Publishing Office (GPO) and the Administrative Office of the United States Courts (AOUSC) to provide public access to opinions from selected United States appellate, district, and bankruptcy courts

image.title: Bankruptcy Court Eastern District of Wisconsin - New items on govinfo

channel.copyright: Title 17, Section 105, United States Code, provides that: Copyright protection under this title is not available for any work of the United States Government, but the United States Government is not precluded from receiving and holding copyrights transferred to it by assignment, bequest, or otherwise. For more information, see https://www.govinfo.gov/about/policies#copyright
